title: NTP Ep. 7 - The Myth of Measuring Up
description:
'I am enough.' It is a message that promises peace but we know deep down inside we fall short. You can quit trying to measure up and we let God's supernatural power be enough. It's the most freeing way to live.

Find the Nothing to Prove Bible study here: https://www.amazon.com/Nothing-Prove-Study-Guide-Streaming-ebook/dp/B08ZMF8QFJ
